scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Information
scopecontent.p: This series of the George Mason University Archives group contains the tabulated results of semester faculty course evaluations administered by the University administration. These materials record the total ratings given GMU instructors by students who had taken their courses.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged by Year/Semester/Discipline or Department/Course Number/Section.
